feedback_text: Ray is working on a new idea related to Wine inventory management/sales. This is an area where he knows stakeholders (i.e.: restaurant/bar owners) and has done some research regarding the needs. He put a lot of thought into how the solution would meet the need. Listening to his Jobs to be done and value proposition I didn't find anything missing but I was able to add insight based on my knowledge of how skus, upcs, and other product number system works.  I suggested there might be an api.  Ray immediately went online to find any and located one which then began to give him other ideas for what to add.  He's already creating a prompt to start.  It's great to watch fellow builders as we grow together and expand our goals with the new information we learn. I look forward to seeing where Ray takes this project.
summary:
Strengths: Ray's thorough research and understanding of stakeholders' needs. Openness to feedback and willingness to explore new ideas.

Additional Comments: Ray's proactive approach and adaptability are commendable. Exciting to see the collaborative learning environment among peers.
